Name: DS Healthcare Group Inc
Description: DS Healthcare Group, Inc. (DS Healthcare) is engaged in developing products for skin care and personal care needs. Divine Skin researches and develops (formulates) its own products. The Company offers a range of products, which include skin care, personal care and hair care. The Company formulates market and sells these products through specialty retailers, spas, salons and other distributors. It conducts its business under the names, such as Divine Skin and the DS Laboratories trade name. It also sells certain products under its Polaris Labs, Sigma Skin and Pure Guild brands. The Company distributes hair care products through its subsidiary, Polaris Labs, Inc. (Polaris). These products are primarily distributed through physicians. In January 2013, the Company acquired Divine Skin Laboratories S.A.
